    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Caius</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リッド</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Reid</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>チェスター</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chester</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なによ、カイウス！
まともにキャンプの用意も出来ないの！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the heck, Caius!
You can't even reasonably prepare our camp?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うるさいな。
そんなに言うんだったら
少しはルビアも手伝えよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shut up already. If you're gonna
complain so much, start helping out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ？
キャンプの準備、手間取ってるのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's going on? Are you guys
having trouble preparing your camp?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ったく、これだから
山に慣れてねぇ奴はよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Geez, this is what happens when people
come up into the mountains and aren't used to it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>手伝うから、貸してみろよ。
オレ達山に入ること多いから
こういうのには慣れてんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We can help, Let us see it. We go into the
mountains pretty often, so we're used to this stuff.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うるさいわね！
カイウスだって本気出せば
このくらい簡単に出来るわよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shut up! If Caius just took this seriously,
it'd be a breeze to get done!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それを出来ない子みたいに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's like an incapable child...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>もう怒った！　勝負よ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now I'm angry! Fight me!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
